{"title":"2024 Builders for Builders Fundraiser to Support More Trails in Lost Sierra","link":"https://bikerumor.com/2024-builders-for-builders-fundraiser-bike-raffle/","date":1718799153000,"content":"<p><img src=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/Builders-for-Builders-Fundraiser-hero.jpeg\" width=\"1200\" height=\"630\" alt=\"(Photos/Souphorse)\" /></p>\n<p>For 2024, the <a href=\"https://givebutter.com/buildersforbuilders\" target=\"_blank\">Builders for Builders</a> Fundraiser is back to benefit the Sierra Butte Trail Stewardship (SBTS). So far the Builders for Builders program has raised over $100,000 to date. The proceeds from the fundraising campaign go back to the Stewardship to support more trails in the Lost Sierra.</p>\n\n\n\n<figure>\n<figure><a href=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/Builders-for-Builders-Fundraiser-builders-Mosaic-and-SyCip.jpg\"><img width=\"453\" height=\"636\" src=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/Builders-for-Builders-Fundraiser-builders-Mosaic-and-SyCip.jpg\" alt=\"Builders for Builders Fundraiser builders Mosaic and SyCip\" srcset=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/Builders-for-Builders-Fundraiser-builders-Mosaic-and-SyCip.jpg 453w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/Builders-for-Builders-Fundraiser-builders-Mosaic-and-SyCip-214x300.jpg 214w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/Builders-for-Builders-Fundraiser-builders-Mosaic-and-SyCip-85x120.jpg 85w\" /></a></figure>\n\n\n\n<figure><a href=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/Builders-for-Builders-Fundraiser-builders-Caletti-and-NeuHaus.jpg\"><img width=\"453\" height=\"638\" src=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/Builders-for-Builders-Fundraiser-builders-Caletti-and-NeuHaus.jpg\" alt=\"Builders for Builders Fundraiser builders Caletti and NeuHaus\" srcset=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/Builders-for-Builders-Fundraiser-builders-Caletti-and-NeuHaus.jpg 453w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/Builders-for-Builders-Fundraiser-builders-Caletti-and-NeuHaus-213x300.jpg 213w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/Builders-for-Builders-Fundraiser-builders-Caletti-and-NeuHaus-85x120.jpg 85w\" /></a></figure>\n</figure>\n\n\n\n<p>Between now and July 2nd, for <a href=\"https://givebutter.com/buildersforbuilders\" target=\"_blank\">every donation made </a>of at least $10, there is a chance to win a custom frame handcrafted by one of the following frame builders.</p>\n\n\n\n<h2>The 2024 Builders</h2>\n\n\n\n<h3><a href=\"https://caletticycles.com/\" target=\"_blank\">Caletti Cycles</a></h3>\n\n\n\n<figure><a href=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/Builders-for-Builders-Fundraiser-Caletti-Cycles.jpeg\"><img width=\"1280\" height=\"961\" src=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/Builders-for-Builders-Fundraiser-Caletti-Cycles.jpeg\" alt=\"Builders for Builders Fundraiser Caletti Cycles\" srcset=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/Builders-for-Builders-Fundraiser-Caletti-Cycles.jpeg 1280w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/Builders-for-Builders-Fundraiser-Caletti-Cycles-297x223.jpeg 297w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/Builders-for-Builders-Fundraiser-Caletti-Cycles-120x90.jpeg 120w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/Builders-for-Builders-Fundraiser-Caletti-Cycles-768x577.jpeg 768w\" /></a><figcaption>(Photos/Souphorse)</figcaption></figure>\n\n\n\n<h3><a href=\"https://www.sycip.com/\" target=\"_blank\">SyCip Bicycles</a></h3>\n\n\n\n<figure><a href=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/Builders-for-Builders-Fundraiser-SyCip-Bicycles.jpeg\"><img width=\"1280\" height=\"965\" src=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/Builders-for-Builders-Fundraiser-SyCip-Bicycles.jpeg\" alt=\"Builders for Builders Fundraiser SyCip Bicycles\" srcset=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/Builders-for-Builders-Fundraiser-SyCip-Bicycles.jpeg 1280w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/Builders-for-Builders-Fundraiser-SyCip-Bicycles-297x224.jpeg 297w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/Builders-for-Builders-Fundraiser-SyCip-Bicycles-120x90.jpeg 120w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/Builders-for-Builders-Fundraiser-SyCip-Bicycles-768x579.jpeg 768w\" /></a></figure>\n\n\n\n<h3><a href=\"https://www.mosaiccycles.com/\" target=\"_blank\">Mosaic Cycles</a></h3>\n\n\n\n<figure><a href=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/Builders-for-Builders-Fundraiser-Mosaic-Cycles.jpeg\"><img width=\"1280\" height=\"989\" src=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/Builders-for-Builders-Fundraiser-Mosaic-Cycles.jpeg\" alt=\"Builders for Builders Fundraiser Mosaic Cycles\" srcset=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/Builders-for-Builders-Fundraiser-Mosaic-Cycles.jpeg 1280w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/Builders-for-Builders-Fundraiser-Mosaic-Cycles-297x229.jpeg 297w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/Builders-for-Builders-Fundraiser-Mosaic-Cycles-120x93.jpeg 120w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/Builders-for-Builders-Fundraiser-Mosaic-Cycles-768x593.jpeg 768w\" /></a></figure>\n\n\n\n<h3><a href=\"https://www.neuhausmetalworks.com/\" target=\"_blank\">NeuHaus Metal Works</a></h3>\n\n\n\n<figure><a href=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/Builders-for-Builders-Fundraiser-NeuHaus-Metal-Works.jpeg\"><img width=\"1280\" height=\"957\" src=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/Builders-for-Builders-Fundraiser-NeuHaus-Metal-Works.jpeg\" alt=\"Builders for Builders Fundraiser NeuHaus Metal Works\" srcset=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/Builders-for-Builders-Fundraiser-NeuHaus-Metal-Works.jpeg 1280w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/Builders-for-Builders-Fundraiser-NeuHaus-Metal-Works-297x222.jpeg 297w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/Builders-for-Builders-Fundraiser-NeuHaus-Metal-Works-120x90.jpeg 120w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/Builders-for-Builders-Fundraiser-NeuHaus-Metal-Works-768x574.jpeg 768w\" /></a></figure>\n\n\n\n<p>The winner will select the fabricator of their choice for the frame, choosing from the list above. That frame will then get custom painted. After which it will then get built with high-end componentry from <a href=\"https://www.paulcomp.com/\" target=\"_blank\">Paul Components</a>, <a href=\"https://www.whiteind.com/\" target=\"_blank\">White Industries</a>, and <a href=\"https://www.wtb.com/\" target=\"_blank\">WTB</a>.</p>\n\n\n\n<h2>Connected Communities</h2>\n\n\n\n<p><em>“The funds will specifically support <a href=\"https://sierratrails.org/connected-communities/\" target=\"_blank\">Connected Communities</a>, SBTS’ plan to connect 15 mountain towns via a 564-mile multi-use singletrack trail. Once completed, these sections of singletrack can be linked with a vast network of existing paved and gravel doubletrack to create a plethora of gravel-bike-friendly bikepacking routes in the Lost Sierra, that dip in and out of local towns for resupply, restaurant, and lodging options.</em></p>\n\n\n\n<p><em>We recently released the <a href=\"https://sierratrails.org/connected-communities-trails-master-plan/\" target=\"_blank\">68-page Trails Master Plan</a> for the project, which outlines the proposed trail, dubbed The Lost Sierra Route, as well as plans to incorporate building techniques to create Fire Hardened Trails to manage vegetation for wildfire mitigation. Connected Communities trail projects are already in the works, but completing the entire project will require a heavy financial lift. </em></p>\n\n\n\n<p><em>Dollars raised through fundraisers such as Builders for Builders are vital, as they bring in unrestricted funds or funds that don’t require a costly match or significant staff resources to manage, as is customary with government grants”.</em> </p>\n<p>The post <a href=\"https://bikerumor.com/2024-builders-for-builders-fundraiser-bike-raffle/\">2024 Builders for Builders Fundraiser to Support More Trails in Lost Sierra</a> appeared first on <a href=\"https://bikerumor.com\">Bikerumor</a>.</p>","author":"Ron Frazelle","siteTitle":"Bikerumor","siteHash":"49f427af0a926f4232eb837006841d7242e153e3afbb590f32e4b104ea3e2718","entryHash":"98e5806ac63e187cc52c37e54301f0d0ed609d7b93ec2463834d5e5860ff9bae","category":"Cycling"}